\c 14
\s Asa mambo waJudha
\p
\v 1 Zvino Abhija wakarara nemadzibaba ake, ivo ndokumuviga muguta raDhavhidhi. Asa mwanakomana wake ndokuva mambo pachinzvimbo chake. Mumazuva ake nyika yaiva murunyararo makore gumi\x + 1 Madz. 15.8.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino Asa wakaita zvakanaka nezvakarurama pameso paJehovha Mwari wake.
\v 3 Nokuti wakabvisa aritari dzeutorwa nenzvimbo dzakakwirira\x + 15.17. 14.5. 1 Madz. 15.14.\x*, ndokuputsa zvifananidzo, ndokutema matanda ekunamata nawo\x + Det. 7.5. 1 Madz. 16.33.\x*.
\v 4 Zvino wakaraira Judha kutsvaka Jehovha Mwari wemadzibaba avo, nekuita mutemo nemurairo.
\v 5 Wakabvisawo kubva mumaguta ese aJudha nzvimbo dzakakwirira nearitari dzezuva. Nyika ndokuva nerunyararo pamberi pake\x + 15.17. 14.5. 1 Madz. 15.14.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Zvino wakavaka maguta akashoshewa kwaJudha; nokuti nyika yaiva ine runyararo\x + 11.5.\x* uye kwaiva kusina hondo naye mumakore awa, nokuti Jehovha waiva amuzorodza\x + 14.1.\x*.
\v 7 Naizvozvo wakati kuna Judha: Ngativake maguta awa, uye tiite rusvingo ku\add a\add*poteredza, neshongwe, masuwo, nemazariro, nyika ichiri pamberi pedu\x + 8.5.\x*; nokuti takatsvaka Jehovha Mwari wedu; taka\add mu\add*tsvaka, akatipa zororo kukomberedza. Zvino vakavaka ndokubudirira\x + 15.15. 20.30.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino Asa waiva nevarwi zvuru mazana matatu kwaJudha, vaiva vakatakura nhovo huru nemapfumo; nezvuru mazana maviri nemakumi masere kwaBhenjamini\x + 13.3.\x*, vaiva vakatakura nhovo vaitsika uta; ava vese vaiva varume vesimba veumhare\x + 1 Makor. 5.18.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Zvino kwakabudira kwaari Zera muItiyopiya\x + 16.8. 12.3.\x* nehondo yechuru chezvuru, nengoro mazana matatu; ndokusvika kuMaresha\x + Josh. 15.44. 11.8.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino Asa wakabuda kuzorwa naye; ivo ndokurongedza hondo pamupata weZefata\x + Vato. 1.17.\x* paMaresha\x + 11.8. Josh. 15.44.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino Asa wakachema kuna Jehovha Mwari wake\x + 13.14. Eki. 14.10. 1 Makor. 5.20. Map. 22.5. Vato. 3.9.\x*, ndokuti: Jehovha kubatsira hachisi chinhu kwamuri, kana kune vakawanda kana kune vasina simba; tibatsirei Jehovha Mwari wedu\x + 1 Sam. 14.6. Vato. 7.7.\x*; nokuti takazembera pamuri\x + 13.18.\x*, uye nezita renyu tauya kurwisana nechaunga ichi; Jehovha, imwi muri Mwari wedu\x + 1 Sam. 17.45.\x*; munhu ngaarege kukukundai\x + 1 Makor. 29.14.\x*.
\v 12 Naizvozvo Jehovha wakarova VaItiyopiya pamberi paAsa, nepamberi paJudha; VaItiyopiya ndokutiza\x + 13.15.\x*.
\v 13 Asa nevanhu vaiva naye ndokuvadzingirira kusvika paGerari\x + Gen.. 10.19. 20.1. 26.1,6.\x*; ndokuwa kubva kuVaItiyopiya zvekuti hakuna kumbova nekumutsiridzika kwavari; nokuti vakaparadzwa pamberi paJehovha nepamberi pehondo yake. Vakatakura zvakapambiwa zvizhinji kwazvo\x + Ezi. 9.8,9.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino vakarova maguta ese akapoteredza Gerari\x + Gen.. 10.19. 20.1. 26.1,6.\x*; nokuti kutya Jehovha kwaiva pavari; zvino vakapamba maguta ese, nokuti maiva mune zvakapambiwa zvizhinji maari\x + 17.10. 20.29. Gen.. 35.5.\x*.
\v 15 Vakarovawo matende ezvipfuwo, ndokutapa makwai mazhinji nemakamera, ndokudzokera kuJerusarema.